I gave this two forks because my kids and hubby liked it but I wasn't overly impressed. It tasted o.k. but I found it a lot of work for o.k. plus with brandy and whipping cream this was pretty expensive for just a mid week dinner. So..... not special enough for company but not worth the work and money for just everyday. I don't think I will make this again.

